{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e86a481758","title":"关于军事系统向中央汇报工作问题的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4048e147be","index":0,"year":1956,"month":12,"day":14,"articleId":"e86a481758"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji37","name":"毛泽东全集第37卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/37-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji37":{"comments":[{"id":"f36889641a","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"e86a481758","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在彭德怀1956年12月13日关于军事系统向中央汇报工作问题给毛泽东的请示报告上。报告说，你在今年夏季说过两次，军事系统各部，也要照政府各部一样，系统地向中央汇报一次工作。我认为这不仅对于中央政治局或常委会的同志了解国防建设是必要的，同时对于军事系统各部、各军种、兵种的同志也是一次很大的鼓励。因八大前后事情很忙，这项工作未能进行，可否在明年1月初句军委扩大会议结束后进行汇报。"},{"id":"df77f5b29d","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"e86a481758","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"彭德怀，当时任中共中央军委委员、国务院副总理兼国防部部长，主持军委日常工作。"}],"contents":[{"id":"ba9d913b05","type":"title","text":"关于军事系统向中央汇报工作问题的批语”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"e86a481758"},{"id":"f36889641a","type":"paragraph","text":"退彭德怀时同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"e86a481758"},{"id":"df77f5b29d","type":"paragraph","text":"可以准备在春季或春夏之间了解几个军事部门的工作情况","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"e86a481758"},{"id":"871654e512","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"e86a481758"},{"id":"6b282018e7","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月十四日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"e86a481758"}],"page":{"id":"fa0bc4553a","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"e86a481758","start":188,"end":188}}}},"__N_SSG":true}